{
  "stem": "8527.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He lived upstairs of us, and he-- the cheder was right in his apartment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I recollect that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I never went to public school, because by the time I was old enough to go to public school, the war was on, and I-- we, as Jews, we couldn't go to public school.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So my education just prior to the war was limited to religious education.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My formal education really didn't start till after the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My family had a butcher shop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My dad and my mother both worked in the butcher shop.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, it was sort of unusual, but my family's shop was-- the clientele was mostly Gentile because our meats were not kosher.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That means it was not for Jewish consumption.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So most of our customers were either the farmers or the Poles in-- in-- within the city.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And therefore, our acquaintances were-- a lot of were Polish people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's probably one of the reasons for my and my sister's survival, because of our acquaintances with the Gentile population.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Apart from your butcher shop business, were you associated with Gentiles at your age, as a child?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Personally, I don't even know whether they were Gentile or Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were kids that we played with.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I do recall the revelation of a Gentile boy, you know, coming up to me and asking me why I killed Christ.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at that time, I didn't know who Christ was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went home and asked my parents who Christ is, and why is he saying that to me?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was probably my first encounter with that type of situation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I lived basically in a Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were pretty well confined to our area.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did mingle with the outside community.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Were you aware of anti-Semitism?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
